006300     PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I > YEARS
006400         MOVE SPACES TO GRAPH-LINE
006500         COMPUTE SCALED-VAL = ((BAL(I) - MIN-BAL) / 
006600                 (MAX-BAL - MIN-BAL)) * 60
